name: Article Content
key: article content
content-length: 1200

<p>Looking smart and cool in the summer months can be a tricky proposition for men. The key is to go for a more relaxed look, and put the emphasis on lightweight, easy-going fabrics – and impeccable tailoring, of course. </p>

<p>Hackett London is an expert at balancing style and comfort, and the British label is offering four special pieces exclusively at its LANDMARK MEN store at LANDMARK ATRIUM that you won’t regret adding to your summer wardrobe. </p>

<p>The Mayfair White Dot jacquard shirt, in 100% cotton and with double cuffs, is a polished item that makes the statement “true gentleman”. It is a perfect match for the single-breasted cotton shirt jacket. The combination of the navy jacket and white shirt is a classic look for summer, bringing in overtones of nautical panache. </p>

<p>Complementing the shirt and jacket are a pair of slim-fit cotton trousers in white – another traditional hot-weather icon. Topping off the outfit is a blue polka dot handkerchief, tucked into the breast pocket. </p>

<p>And there you have it – a sophisticated, elegant, yet laid-back look that will take a gentleman everywhere, from summer garden parties and alfresco dining to boating trips. </p>

